    "Leaky integrate and fire model.",
    "As already mentioned, LIF models are popularly used to mimic the spiking behavior of a neuron.",
    "The evolution of membrane potential, u(t) in an LIF model can be written as 12, 34 τ du dt",
    "where τ is the \"leaky\" time constant of the membrane, R is the membrane resistance, I(t) is the injected current, and v rest is the resting potential of the cell.",
    "In discrete time for spiking input Eq."
